description: Foodies of Los Angeles, if you’re on the lookout for incredible Asian cuisine that’s fresh and refined, roam no further because you share a home with Mastermind.With a carefully-crafted menu that features our favorite Fusion dishes like flavorful BBQ Pork Rice, Spicy Mini Lobster Rice, delicious Pork & Chicken Banh Mi, and more, trust us that it takes an absolute Mastermind to serve high-quality food that’s this tasty and fast.
name: Mastermind
